  <ul class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
    <li class="p-4 border border-gray-700 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 hover:border-yellow-400 transition">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Minecraft Setups</h3>
      <p>Pre-built server setups, plugins, configs, and more — ready to go.</p>
    </li>
    <li class="p-4 border border-gray-700 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 hover:border-yellow-400 transition">
